   Benjamin Helmich-Paris : MC-RPA, TRAH-SCF, COSX integrals
   Lee Huntington         : MR-EOM, pCC
   Robert Izsak           : Overlap fitted RIJCOSX, COSX-SCS-MP3, EOM
